 <tbody>
  <row>
    <entry>Locate the “equals” word(s).</entry>
    <entry morerows="1"><media id="eip-id1168467129923" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_02_03_032-01.png"/></media></entry>
  </row>
  <row> 
    <entry>Write the = sign.</entry>
    <entry/>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>Translate the words to the left of the <emphasis effect="italics">equals</emphasis> word into an algebraic expression.</entry>
    <entry><media id="eip-id1168468302171" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_02_03_032-02.png"/></media></entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>Translate the words to the right of the <emphasis effect="italics">equals</emphasis> word into an algebraic expression.</entry>
    <entry><media id="eip-id1168468630360" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_02_03_032-03.png"/></media></entry>
  </row>
</tbody>

</tgroup>
</table></para></solution>
</exercise></example>
<note id="fs-id2150330" class="try">
<exercise id="fs-id2751334">
<problem id="fs-id4337605">
<para id="fs-id1885656">Translate the sentence into an algebraic equation:</para>
<para id="fs-id2876785">The sum of <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> gives <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id2647143">
