<example id="fs-id1951299"><exercise id="fs-id1714226">
<problem id="fs-id2268477">
<para id="fs-id2129414">Translate the sentence into an algebraic equation: The product of <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> and <m:math><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:math> is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>56</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
