  <row>
    <entry>Translate the words to the right of the <emphasis effect="italics">equals</emphasis> word into an algebraic expression.</entry>
    <entry><media id="eip-id1168469862456" alt="."><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_02_03_028_img-03.png"/></media></entry>
  </row>
</tbody>

</tgroup>
</table></para></solution>
</exercise></example><note id="fs-id1160008" class="try">
<exercise id="fs-id1587742">
<problem id="fs-id1510864">
<para id="fs-id2454035">Translate the sentence into an algebraic equation:</para>
<para id="fs-id1518700">The product of <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> and <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>54</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
