</note>
<note id="fs-id1171104068967" class="try">
<exercise id="fs-id1381605">
<problem id="fs-id1579337">
<para id="fs-id1171104462746">Translate and solve:</para>
<para id="fs-id1531703">Eleven more than <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> is equal to <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>28</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
