<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id2261028">
<term>solution of an equation</term>
<meaning id="fs-id2819300">A solution to an equation is a value of a variable that makes a true statement when substituted into the equation.
The process of finding the solution to an equation is called solving the equation.
</meaning>
</definition>

</glossary>
